{"tid":580751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"岑麗香恨生B：已經每晚中出  唯有交畀神","createTime":"2018-03-04T18:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T12:05:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":48,"dislike":130,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"0c14b259cca9fea107850ba9b652e695743e522f","tid":580751,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:00:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180304/s00007/1520166181489\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180304%2Fs00007%2F1520166181489&d=pEmv80Ww3uRh8MVoZrTHP%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=35c799df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180304%2Fs00007%2F1520166181489&h=80ee7abd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180304/s00007/1520166181489</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180304/s00007/6999f00bd7608de186865a8ffd52e94c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180304%2Fs00007%2F6999f00bd7608de186865a8ffd52e94c.jpg&h=e4f1e2fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【今日直擊】岑麗香、陳煒及馮盈盈等，今日到將軍澳為新劇《果欄中的江湖大嫂》宣傳，香香低胸性感到場，她表示劇中有場泳衣性感戲，會否擔心如《波士早晨》林泳淘的泳衣戲被blur？她說：「我應該OK的，小朋友睇得，因為劇中角色是教師，所以密實點，性感的都交給盈盈。」<br />\n<br />\n談到好姊妹鍾嘉欣日前報喜，宣布懷第2胎，香香表示嘉欣之前亦跟她們幾位好姊妹分享，稱嘉欣今次佗得辛苦過上一次：「我們唯有為她祈禱，希望她舒服一點，因為我們做姊妹也幫不到太多，希望有假期可以飛過去。」她笑言自己暫時未追到對方，不過將來都想生BB：「不要給壓力我，我會繼續努力的，順其自然交給神。（不是交給強強？)交給神，神始終都是最大。」"},{"pid":"46dd44162c67824f7912fd5428170a55c4dac8c4","tid":580751,"uid":36478,"like":506,"dislike":8,"score":498,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b5fc6fcc825c5189afd7c51ac8dddc110d2448","tid":580751,"uid":53837,"like":606,"dislike":2,"score":604,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:06:56.000Z","msg":"條仔幾好     晚晚中出  又唔怕有bb"},{"pid":"e139bc40b908921fb5